<div class="container">
	<h2>IMPLEMENTS gdpr options and web3.eth,.net,.db and .personal Management API</h2>
	
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12 pt-4 mt-0">

			<h3 id="gdpr">GDPR Options</h3>
			<p>
				This part includes options that are compliant with GDPR.
			</p>
			<div class="col-12">
				<h4>
					General GDPR Options
				</h4>
				<form method='POST' action='/tools'>
					<div class="input-group form-group">
						<input type="checkbox" name="notifications" class="form-check-input" value="true" id="f-notification">
						<label for="f-notification">Would you like to be informed by email for any events concerning your account?</label>
					</div>
					<div class="input-group form-group">
						<input type="checkbox" name="mana" class="form-check-input" value="true" id="f-mana">
						<label for="f-mana">Would you like to let Mana analyze your data to personalize your user experience?</label>
					</div>
					<div class="input-group form-group">
						<input type="checkbox" name="research" class="form-check-input" value="true" id="f-research">
						<label for="f-research">Would you like to allow public research institutes to access your data?</label>
					</div>


					<!-- <div class="input-group form-group">

						<input type="text" name="token" class="form-control" placeholder="verification token" required>
					</div> -->

					<div class="form-group">
						<input type="submit" value="Save" class="btn btn_own_style">
					</div>

				</form>
			</div>

		<hr>

			<div class="col-12">
				<h4>
					Request a copy of your data
				</h4>
				<form method='POST' action='/request'>
						<div class="input-group form-group">
							<input type="checkbox" name="summary" class="form-check-input" value="true" id="f-notification">
							<label for="f-notification">Only a summary of the data</label>
						</div>


						<div class="input-group form-group">
							<label class="sr-only" for="f-verification">Input verification token</label>
							<input type="text" id="f-verification" name="token" class="form-control" placeholder="verification token" required>
						</div>

						<div class="form-group">
							<label class="sr-only">I woul like to get a copy of all my data</label>
							<input type="submit" value="Request" class="btn btn_own_style">
						</div>

				</form>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
	<hr>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12 pt-4 mt-0">

				<h3 id="personal">Personal</h3>
				<p>
					This part includes personal related option for the web3.personal library.
				</p>

		</div>
	</div>
	<hr>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12 pt-4 mt-0">

				<h3 id="ethereum">Ethereum Blockchain</h3>
				<p>
					This part includes ethereum blockchain related methods from the web3.eth library.
				</p>

		</div>
	</div>
	<hr>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12 pt-4 mt-0">

				<h3 id="network">Network Status</h3>
				<p>
				This part includes the node's network status related methods from the web3.net library. As long as I do not run a local node, this option 						is unnecessary.
				</p>

		</div>
	</div>
	<hr>
	<div class="row">
		<div class="col-md-12 pt-4 mt-0">

				<h3 id="db">LevelDB</h3>
				<p>
					This part includes local LevelDB related methods from the web3.db library. As Long as I do not run a local node, this option is 								unnecessary.
				</p>

		</div>
	</div>



</div>

